      <title>市场低迷之际中国股票回购创三年新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/china-share-buybacks-climb-to-three-year-high-amid-market-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国企业正在加大股票回购力度，在不断扩大的救援行动中发挥自己的作用，以阻止全球第二大股市7万亿美元的暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/china-share-buybacks-climb-to-three-year-high-amid-market-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 00:43:43 GMT</pubDate>
